---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="Ajay Malghan is an Indian-American artist working in cameraless photography, abstract and documentary image-making, film, and painting. Based in Rockville, Maryland."
>
  <section class="about">
    <h1 class="display about__h">About</h1>

    <div class="about__body prose">
      <p>
        I'm an Indian-American artist and the son of first-generation immigrant
        parents. I've exhibited across the country and lectured in Hong Kong,
        India, and a range of universities in the US. I've been a practicing
        musician since the age of six, and I'm one half of the band
        <a href="/music">Limo Tinted Sun</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        My work is held in the private collections of Johns Hopkins University,
        the University of Texas, and Georgetown University.
      </p>
      <p>
        Over the years my work has been featured in publications including
        <a href="https://oxfordamerican.org/eyes/devil-x2019-s-half-acre" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Oxford American</a>,
        <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/in-the-galleries-a-homage-to-hillary-is-repurposed/2016/12/15/da55781e-c09f-11e6-897f-918837dae0ae_story.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the Washington Post</a>,
        <a href="https://www.wired.com/2014/08/ajay-malghan-bleached/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Wired</a>,
        <a href="http://www.npr.org/sections/thesalt/2013/06/09/178444120/an-abstract-look-at-the-food-we-eat" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NPR</a>,
        <a href="https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/9anqdz/mulching-pictures-is-natures-photoshop" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vice</a>, and elsewhere.
      </p>
      <p>
        I live in Rockville, Maryland, where I also run
        <a href="https://www.aharamushrooms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ahara Mushrooms</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about__contact">
      <span class="about__contact-label">Contact</span>
      <a href="mailto:ajaymalghan@gmail.com" class="about__email">ajaymalghan@gmail.com</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 64ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) var(--page-x);
  }
  .about__h {
    font-size: var(--t-6);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .about__body { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .about__body p { font-size: var(--t-3); }
  .about__contact {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .about__contact-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--t-1);
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .about__email {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--t-3);
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    display: inline-block;
    width: max-content;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .about__email:hover { border-color: var(--ink); }
</style>
